Lovers on Monday painted cities and towns red as they celebrate valentines day with their loved ones. On this day lovers expect to receive something out of the ordinary from their partners. Valentines day is one themed with love. Roses, gifts, dinners, and getaways are some of the ways lovers use to show appreciation to their partners. Flower vendors are expected to reap big from the sale of the flowers as lovers rush to buy flowers for their families, partners and friends. In Voi, Taita Taveta County a bouquet of flowers sells at Sh500 while a single rose is sold at Sh100.